# Keep the root build context small. Design-asset folders are untracked, so a
# git-based build (Coolify) won't include them anyway; these guards cover local
# `docker build .` from the repo root too.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.astro
**/.vercel
**/.netlify
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/_shot.mjs
.git
.DS_Store

# Design deliverables / source docs — not needed to build the site.
Home Page/
Learning Center/
Logo/
__Revisions/
Sub-Category Programs/
knowledge-base/
docs/
*.pdf
*.zip
*.csv
